727940f-b.title: Queens: Roosevelt Avenue - Union Street
727940f-b.text:
Roosevelt Avenue, north side, between Union and Main Streets,
Flushing, showing the old Armory of the 17th Separate Company, New
York National Guard, erected in 1894. It is a brick and wood struc-
ture.
